e in a test environment, and I can always recreate it later if needed.\n\nAlternatively, I could patch the webhook to use a namespace selector that excludes the `demo` namespace.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2551,"cache_read_input_tokens":62480,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2551},"output_tokens":22,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7528de2a-04ad-4ee1-8791-50b7cb9b61fc","uuid":"01e2ecac-018b-44a9-91dd-214ecf848774","request_id":"req_011CcQ1w9qcezA5kvSosjMdK"}
